songs.full_title: I Was Jack (You Were Diane) by Jake Owen
songs.title: I Was Jack (You Were Diane)

description.plain: This song was directly inspired by the song “Jack & Diane”  which is a 1982 hit rock song written and performed by American singer-songwriter John Mellencamp, then performing as “John Cougar.” The beat of the song has a similar sound to John Mellencamps song, and Jake Owen refers to many parts of the original song in his song.
